&lt;h3&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct cutting-edge alpha and strategy research using state-of-the-art ML and statistical&lt;br&gt;modeling techniquesGenerate innovative alpha ideas and explore new datasets in a collaborative environment&lt;/li&gt;
